    "brand_story_combo_JeTTXn": {
      "type": "brand-story-combo",
      "name": "Story Layout Bundle",
      "settings": {
        "layout": "image-left",
        "width": "wrapper",
        "top_heading": "<p><strong>And to do that you had to travel the world?</strong></p>",
        "top_text": "<p>To learn the craft, I traveled the world. I visited over a thousand factories—Italian and international—and studied under master artisans. Each experience was invaluable. Yet I realized that to truly succeed, I couldn't simply follow their path. I had to forge my own. I had to become Roberto.<strong><br/><br/>\"Flowers represent romanticism, they are a symbol of love.\"</strong></p>",
