    "brand_split_row_chpbUh": {
      "type": "brand-split-row",
      "name": "Image Text Split",
      "settings": {
        "width": "wrapper",
        "layout": "image-right",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/roberto-coin-kuala-lumpur.png",
        "text": "<p><strong>WHY IS IT SO IMPORTANT THAT YOU ALWAYS CREATE SOMETHING NEW?</strong></p><p>I don’t like standardization and I have always wanted my jewels to be unique. Continuous innovation is essential — it means to go forward. And it is not only about jewels — it is about giving a future to culture.</p><p>Beauty is really everywhere. We are surrounded by it. It has always been my mission to search continuously for beauty — and to share it.</p>",
        "padding_top": 120,
        "padding_bottom": 0
      }
